DB Access Tutorial

step0 - Direct access using java.sql.* namespace
 - used only org.postgresql dependency to define driver
 - to launch example:
    - execute sql/schema.sql file
    - execute sql/test-data.sql file

step1 - Spring-JDBC access using spring-framework
 - added spring-jdbc dependency
 - to launch example:
    - execute sql/schema.sql file
    - execute sql/test-data.sql file

step2 - JPA with Hibernate implementation
 - to launch example:
    - execute sql/schema.sql file
    - execute sql/test-data.sql file